OL,3,CPolice dealing with incident at school
OL,4,Cin Ystradgynlais
OL,6,FPolice are attending an ongoing
OL,7,Fincident at a comprehensive school in
OL,8,FYstradgynlais.
OL,10,FDyfed-Powys Police said officers were
OL,11,Fcalled to Maesydderwen Comprehensive
OL,12,FSchool at approximately 10:45 on
OL,13,FMonday 2nd, March.
OL,15,FOfficers remain at the scene, but no
OL,16,Finformation has yet been provided on
OL,17,Fthe nature of the incident.
