OL,3,CPolice dealing with incident at school
OL,4,Cin Ystradgynlais
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are dealing with an incident at
OL,8,FMaesydderwen Comprehensive School in
OL,9,FYstradgynlais, following a report made
OL,10,Fat approx 10.45am this morning.
OL,12,F"Officers are in attendance. More
OL,13,Fupdates to follow."
